69
00:04:45,600 --> 00:05:12,520
 [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

70
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:30,560
 [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

71
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:34,040
 Verse 7, there came a woman of Samaria to draw water.

72
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:36,680
 Jesus said to her, give me a drink.

73
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:40,400
 For his disciple had gone away into the city to buy food.

74
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:42,880
 The Samaritan woman said to him, how is it

75
