 that you, a Jew, ask a drink of me, a woman of Samaria?

76
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:51,120
 For Jews have no dealings with the Samaritans.

77
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,960
 So Jesus answered her, if you knew the gift of God

