 Where do you get the living water?

84
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:39,820
 [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

85
00:06:39,820 --> 00:06:45,440
 Are you greater than our father Jacob who gave us the well

86
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:49,220
 and drank from it himself and his sons and his cattle?

87
00:06:49,220 --> 00:06:52,240
 Jesus said to her, everyone who drinks of this water

88
